metadata.name: Circumpolarity
metadata.description:
There are shooting stars all around us;  we need only change our perspective to see it.  
  
This is the very first star trail timelapse video I ever created.  It wasn't in the wilderness or anywhere you'd know about...  Just out of frame below is my parents' garage!  Talk about humble origins...  
  
---  
  
**Artist:**  Steve Walasavage  
**Series:**  This And That  
**Collection:**  SW Special Editions  
**Edition:**  1/5 NFT  
  
---  
  
*"SW Special Editions"* is a set of fascinating special editions released as a series of rewards/airdrops/bonuses for certain collectors, patrons, and supporters.  These pieces are intended to be more of a set of keepsakes and mementos than actual artwork, though many pieces *are* artwork as well.  Think of these as milestones, rare moments, firsts, and treasures, available only to my most avid supporters!  
  
All editions are ERC-1155 tokens minted on the [SW Special Editions](https://etherscan.io/address/0x6eEEC1e9442A8023fBF94243C575dB8F815e96BF) custom smart contract.
